correctness.rationale: Major schema and factual issues across both processes. Key problems: (1) Numerous schema violations due to nulls/placeholder text where numbers/objects are required: pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, thicknessControl.filmThickness, processParameters.filmThickness, nucleationPeriod, all flowRates numericValues, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, roughness.value, filmDensity.value, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values.quantityValue, atomicRatio.elements/value, deviceProperties subfields, plasmaPower, and supercycleDesign are set to None or 'Not Found' instead of valid values or omitted when optional. (2) Dosing/purge times use wrong units/magnitudes: article reports 1.65 s reactant and 4.4 s N2 purge; schema unit is MilliSEC, so values must be 1650 ms and 4400 ms, not 1.65 and 4.4. (3) Electrical resistivity uses wrong units/numbers: article gives 0.53 Ω·cm (Film A) and 14.7 Ω·cm (Film B); schema unit is OHM-M, so values must be 0.0053 and 0.147 Ω·m, not 0.53 and 14.7 Ω·m. (4) Missing co-reactant for Process B: O2 is explicitly pulsed before H2O (DEZ/N2/O2/H2O/N2) but reactantSelection.coReactant lists only H2O; dosingTime also omits the separate O2 pulse. (5) Unsubstantiated/guessed fields: saturation=True and carrierGas=N2 are not explicitly stated as saturation or carrier gas in the article (N2 is purge gas). (6) Optional fields incorrectly populated with None (e.g., plasmaPower, supercycleDesign, deviceProperties subfields) should be omitted, not set to null. (7) Film thickness left null despite being inferable and required in thicknessControl: ≈618 nm for Film A (3000×2.06 Å) and ≈414 nm for Film B (3000×1.38 Å); values should be provided with NanoM units if used. Correct by removing/omitting optional fields instead of nulls, adding O2 as a co-reactant to Process B, fixing time units, converting resistivity to Ω·m, and populating required numeric fields or leaving out properties that are not required by the schema.

completeness.rationale: Major incompleteness and multiple schema violations. Key issues: (1) Missing processes: the article reports three ZnO ALD sequences at 180 °C (A: DEZ/N2/H2O/N2; B: DEZ/N2/O2/H2O/N2; C: DEZ/N2/H2O/O2/N2) and additional DEZ+O2-only processes at 230 and 280 °C with reported GPCs (0.1 and 0.36 Å/cycle) and (002) orientation. The extraction includes only A and B and omits C and the O2-only cases. (2) Reactant/co-reactant inconsistency: Process B uses both O2 and H2O as oxidants but the coReactant list contains only H2O; dosing/purge entries also fail to reflect the added O2 step. (3) Time-unit errors: The article gives 1.65 s dose and 4.4 s purge; the schema unit is MilliSEC, but the extraction uses numeric values 1.65 and 4.4 with unit MilliSEC (1000× too small). Should be 1650 ms and 4400 ms. (4) Resistivity unit conversion errors: Reported values are 0.53 and 14.7 Ω·cm, but the extraction uses unit OHM-M with the same numeric values; they must be converted to 0.0053 and 0.147 Ω·m, respectively. (5) Required numeric fields left null: processParameters.pressure, flowRates.*.quantityValue.numericValue, nucleationPeriod, thicknessControl.filmThickness, and numerous materialProperties (uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values, roughness.value, filmDensity.value) are null, violating the schema and the “no nulls” requirement. (6) Invalid/placeholder values: saturation is set to True without textual support; deliveryMethod and safety are "Not Found"; otherAspects.filmStability and reproducibility are null booleans; deviceProperties fields are set to null objects. (7) Structural/schema issues: processParameters includes an extra top-level filmThickness not defined by the schema; plasmaPower and supercycleDesign are present as null instead of being omitted. (8) Traceability gaps: O2 co-reactant for B is not captured; growth mode/orientation changes linked to oxygen sequencing are not represented in any field. To improve completeness: add separate process objects for Film C and the DEZ+O2-only depositions (230 and 280 °C) with correct temperatures and GPCs; include O2 as coReactant and dosing/purge times for B and C; correct time units to ms; convert resistivity units; supply non-null required numeric fields or omit optional properties; remove null-typed fields (plasmaPower, supercycleDesign, deviceProperties) and any properties not in the schema; if film thickness is required, compute from GPC×cycles or leave unspecified only if allowed by the schema.
